  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then because of the family of my mother, who were, as I said, they were-- they were very active and they had-- and two brothers of my mother, or even three brothers of my mother, were having those textile workshops, which and they must have had some access to food or to-- and-- and we still managed to exist in a relatively not deprived manner.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "However, we were-- the flat where we lived in Chlodna-- I think 49 or 41, I'm not sure-- became then taken out of the whole house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, the whole group of houses was taken out of the ghetto, and that happened a number of times that the streets which were on the-- almost on the outskirts of the ghetto near the wall, where suddenly the Germans decreed that the ghetto has to be reduced in size.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a few streets or a groups of houses were taken out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they suddenly decided that this part of the Chlodna was taken out, and we had to move out of there very quickly, and we still managed to get some of our things and most of our things, I think, and furniture that we had there into some other places.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had for a while no place to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's the end of tape number four.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is it four?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
